Automation is the crucial need for Devops practices. Automation in DevOps boosts speed, consistency, higher accuracy, reliability and increase in number of 
deliveries.

Version Control Tool - GIT (GitHub, GitLab, Bitbucket)
Build tool - Maven, gradle, MS Build(dotnet)
Continous Integration tool - Jenkins (Deployment automation)
Configuration Management tool - Chef, Puppet, Ansible
Containerization - Docker
Container Orcestration - Kubernetes
Testing tool - Selenium, Gremlin
Monitoring tool - Nagios, New Relic
Log Management - Splunk
Infrastructure automation - AWS
